description:
Supplementary table referenced in Chapter 4 of my PhD thesis. 
   Table caption:   
  Table S2: Differential expression analysis results (RNA-seq).&nbsp;  
 Table contains all genes that were significantly differentially expressed (adjusted p-value &lt; 0.05 for a |log2 fold change| &gt; 1) in the hna+ strain (M2884) relative to the hna&ndash; strain (M2882), ranked by log2-fold change (LFC). Genes with LFC &gt; 1 or &lt; &ndash;1 are indicated in green or red, respectively.&nbsp; 
 &nbsp;

